            <div class="faq-item">
                <div class="faq-question">How long should my YouTube description be?</div>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <p>YouTube allows up to 5,000 characters in descriptions. We recommend using at least 200-300 words with a good mix of keywords, links, and information. The first 2-3 lines are most important as they appear before the "Show more" button.</p>
                </div>
